data.description: Large, partially wooded lot for lots of privacy in Stonebrook Subdivision. Southeast Bulloch school district. Open floor plan. New luxury vinyl plank and carpet. 4 bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms including a master suite with two closets and tray ceiling. Huge bedroom with vaulted ceiling and walk in closet or bonus room. Upgraded lighting throughout home. Stainless steel refrigerator, dishwasher just a few months old, microwave a year old. Spacious pantry, Tile backsplash, upgraded stainless steel single bowled sink and faucet. Water softener. Home on cul de sac. One of the owners has qualified for their GA Real Estate License
